<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="./assets/favicon.png" />
        <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
        <title>Blog Home</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <!-- navigation -->
        <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-10 bg-orange-300 shadow-md">
            <div
                class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 lg:px-0 flex justify-between py-3 items-center"
            >
                <a href="#">
                    <img
                        class="h-10"
                        src="https://learnwithsumit.com/_next/static/media/lws-logo-dark.8e393acf.svg"
                        alt="Learn with Sumit"
                    />
                </a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <section class="relative pt-8 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:pt-16 lg:pb-16 lg:px-10">
            <div class="absolute inset-0">
                <div class="bg-white h-1/3 sm:h-2/3"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto pt-12 sm:pt-5">
                <div class="text-center">
                    <h2
                        class="text-3xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl"
                    >
                        Single Post & Related Posts
                    </h2>
                    <p
                        class="mt-3 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-xl text-gray-500 sm:mt-4"
                    >
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing
                        elit. Ipsa libero labore natus atque, ducimus sed.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- single post  -->
                <div class="flex w-[580px] h-[210px] my-3 mx-auto rounded-lg drop-shadow-lg overflow-auto">
                    <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                        <img
                            class="h-full w-50 object-cover"
                            src="<%= data?.singleDataPost?.imgUrl || 'https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/73503432?v=4' %>"
                            alt="Fake Image"
                        />
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="flex-1 bg-white p-6 flex flex-col justify-between"
                    >
                        <div class="flex-1">
                            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-400">
                                <span
                                    class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800"
                                >
                                    <%= data?.singleDataPost?.imageTitle || "Image Fake Title" %>
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="block mt-1">
                                <p
                                    class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900"
                                >
                                    <%= data?.singleDataPost?.title || "Post Title" %>
                                </p>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <p class="my-2 w-[150px] mx-auto text-center text-md text-indigo-800 border border-indigo-500 bg-indigo-100 rounded-lg">Post Body</p>
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                                <img
                                    class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full"
                                    src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/73503432?v=4"
                                    alt=""
                                />
                            </div>
                            <div class="ml-3">
                                <p
                                    class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 hover:underline"
                                >
                                    <% if(data?.singleDataPost?.body){%>
                                        <%= data?.singleDataPost?.body?.substring(0, 100) || "Post Body" %>
                                    <%}else{ %>
                                        Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Inventore ipsam necessitatibus 
                                        voluptatem, molestias pariatur natus minima. Commodi sequi veritatis, impedit dolorum molestias quam saepe vero earum inventore porro quae natus animi accusamus nobis quos alias. Aspernatur sit aliquam earum quos explicabo, quia consequuntur, soluta aliquid accusamus autem sequi molestiae illo voluptatibus optio. Ratione, sunt laborum. Ut magni rem quasi veritatis labore ipsam iste nemo quas illum numquam a facere molestiae id illo sint cupiditate, quis corporis commodi assumenda iure non! Nihil dolore reiciendis velit. Fugiat nostrum incidunt consequatur dolorem neque? Deleniti dolore dolorum omnis tempora cumque accusamus. Eius quam nulla blanditiis molestiae unde possimus quis aspernatur laudantium soluta aperiam excepturi laborum dolorum temporibus dolorem harum perspiciatis distinctio labore necessitatibus, voluptatem repudiandae dignissimos ducimus reprehenderit. Molestiae temporibus iste tempora vitae nemo! Molestiae velit voluptatibus rem non sed eligendi 
                                        alias voluptate officia natus eum quidem hic ipsa earum, rerum laborum accusantium cum?
                                    <%} %>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto grid gap-5 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:max-w-none">
                    <!-- related posts  -->
                    <% data?.relatedDataPosts?.forEach(post => {%>
                        <div
                            class="flex flex-col rounded-lg drop-shadow-xl overflow-hidden"
                        >
                            <div
                                class="flex-1 bg-white p-6 flex flex-col justify-between"
                            >
                                <div class="flex-1">
                                    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-indigo-600">
                                        <span
                                            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-800"
                                        >
                                            Related Post
                                        </span>
                                        <span
                                            class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-0.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium bg-green-100 text-green-800"
                                        >
                                            Post Id: <%= post.id %>
                                        </span>
                                    </p>
                                    <div class="block mt-1">
                                        <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">
                                            <%= post.title || "Post Title" %>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <hr class="border-b-1 border-gray-100" />
                                <div>
                                    <p
                                        class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 hover:underline"
                                    >
                                    <%= post?.body?.substring(0, 100) || "Post Body" %>
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    <% }); %>
                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- footer -->
        <section class="pt-6 bg-orange-200">
            <div
                class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 py-6 lg:px-0 flex justify-between gap-2 border-t text-sm text-slate-400"
            >
                <div>Copyright 2022 Learn with Sumit.</div>
                <div>
                    <a
                        href="https://youtube.com/learnwithsumit"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noreferrer"
                    >
                        YouTube Channel
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </body>
</html>
